Package: unicefData
Title: Download Indicators from UNICEF Data Warehouse
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joao Pedro", "Azevedo", email = "jazevedo@unicef.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Garen", "Avanesian", role = "aut"))
Description: A bilingual R and Python client to fetch SDMX CSV series from
    UNICEF's Data Warehouse. Features include automatic pagination, caching
    with memoisation, country name lookups, metadata versioning (vintages),
    and comprehensive indicator support for SDG monitoring.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
